Great salad place in the heart of FiDi. Service is fast and has good options for customization.

This is by far my favorite place to get chopped salads. The variety is good and the salads always taste fresh. You get a good serving for your money as well. They have some creative salad mixes and delicious dressings to choose from. You can also ask them to turn your salad into a wrap. My only issue is that the way you order and get your salad chopped can be hectic and confusing, but they try to help you when they can. Overall, if you really want a salad, this would be a good place to go.
Great salads and great service.

Chopt visit this evening was rather disappointing. I made it in about an hour before close and they were out of a number of items. I ended up getting the harvest bowl and it was sad. Brussel sprouts and sweet potatoes I think had passed their prime. Also the server drowned my bowl in the two sauces, I definitely don't need to order this again.
